Refer to this tutorial: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=d2RxKTKldfI&t=225s

The files and folders in the video => The files implemented here:

./config/passport.js                = ./server/service/passport.js
./middleware/auth.js                = ./server/middleware/auth.js
./models/user.js                    = ./server/models/register_model.js
./routes/index.js                   = ./server/routes/frontpage_router.js
./routes/user.js                    = ./server/routes/auth_router.js
./views/dashboard.ejs               = ./views/frontpage2.ejs
./views/login.ejs                   = ./views/login.ejs
./app.js                            = ./server.js
